title: State Farm Gamerhood Challenge
overview: Dive into the ultimate gaming neighborhood where streaming superstars compete in an electrifying mash-up of esports, physical challenges, and unexpected insurance-themed mishaps. Each season, a diverse cast of high-profile gamers and content creators face off in live-streamed challenges—ranging from trivia and online gaming to yard-style stunts—with comedic obstacles built into the set to metaphorically reflect the role of insurance in everyday life
